      <reaction compartment="compartment_876" fast="false" id="reaction_1524186" metaid="metaid_93" name="Phosphorylation of PLCgamma by PDGFR" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The activated PDGF receptor phosphorylates PLCgamma on tyrosine residues 472,771,783 and 1254, activating the enzyme.</p>
        </notes>
