      <reaction compartment="compartment_984" fast="false" id="reaction_382057" metaid="metaid_98" name="Release of novel PDGFs as latent factors" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Novel PDGFs both PDGF-CC and PDGF-DD dimers are secreted as latent factors without removal of the N-terminal CUB domain. These require further activation by extracellular proteolysis.</p>
        </notes>
