      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_380780" metaid="metaid_100" name="Activation of Src" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Activation of Src kinases involves displacement of Tyr527 from the SH2 domain and phosphorylation of other tyrosine residues in the kinase domain. Src activation appears to be important for the mitogenic response of PDGF.</p>
        </notes>
